The paper proposes a training flow for deep neural networks that improves optimization performance and achieves better results on tasks such as image classification, caption generation, and speech recognition. These tasks are typically associated with the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
